Timothy Farrell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timothy_Farrell 0 Timothy Farrell (June 26, 1922 – May 9, 1989) was an American film actor, best known for his roles in the Ed Wood films such as Jail Bait, The Violent Years and Glen or Glenda. He also was the County Marshal of Los Angeles, California.
